---
title: Smart Smoky Mustard Chicken Thighs  with Carrot Mash and Roasted Brussels Sprouts
description: Juicy chicken gets slathered with a smoky and zippy chipotle-mustard sauce that ramps up the flavour, while carrot mash adds both sweetness and savouriness to this nourishing smart meal.

